text.__SUMMARY__: Fargoa bartschi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Pyramidellidae, the pyrams and their allies.
text.Distribution:
This species occurs in the following locations:
Cobscook Bay
Gulf of Maine
Gulf of Mexico
North West Atlantic
text.Notes:
